ake advantage of her."],[10777,10894,"But I've never felt this way"],[10894,11015,"about any girl before."],[11098,11181,"Does she feel the same?"],[11361,11498,"Because all those guys were looking"],[11498,11628,"like they wanted to eat you up."],[11720,11807,"Okay, you don't know the effect"],[11807,11903,"that you have on them."],[12032,12237,"And do I have that effect on you?"],[12353,12487,"I mean, if I didn't know any better,"],[12487,12579,"I'd say"],[12579,12741,"that you're jealous."],[12804,12929,"No, I..."]],"8":[[1985,2047,"Sorry."],[2106,2285,"It's okay, I wanna keep kissing you."],[2285,2339,"I just-"],[2373,2427,"What the fuck is"],[2427,2510,"wrong with you, Cole?"],[2535,2652,"Her brother is your best friend."],[2748,2823,"That was a mistake,"],[2823,2923,"and that can never happen again."],[2994,3061,"Why not?"],[3094,3203,"You're too young for me anyways."],[3203,3303,"You're, you're like a little girl."],[3311,3478,"You are barely older than me."],[3507,3611,"I mean, you weren't looking at me"],[3611,3691,"like I was too young"],[3691,3782,"for you a second ago."],[3782,3953,"Kaitlyn, this cannot happen."],[3978,4045,"Go to bed."],[4045,4237,"You can't send me to bed like a child, Cole."],[4237,4375,"I can and I just did, Katie."],[4396,4533,"Because you're acting like a child."],[5009,5125,"This is Ryan's little sister."],[5167,5267,"I can't do this to him."],[5326,5492,"Why do you still want him, Kaitlyn?"],[5538,5638,"You will always be"],[5638,5805,"his best friend's little sister."],[6322,6406,"Forget what I said."],[6452,6535,"I need you."],[6877,7019,"I want to hear you scream my name,"],[7082,7157,"from these lips"],[7157,7198,"all"],[7265,7298,"night"],[7315,7365,"long."],[7557,7615,"Cole."],[7757,7845,"Kaitlyn!"],[8900,9138,"Great, your first time having sex with Cole,"],[9138,9271,"and it was just a dream."],[9597,9680,"Cold!"],[9984,10035,"Cole."],[10143,10206,"Are you okay?"]],"9":[[29,83,"Are you okay?"],[83,183,"Cole."],[375,458,"C