urn."],[3207,3311,"You were elated to see"],[3311,3420,"that I was your TA."],[3495,3578,"Wrong, Hart."],[3624,3678,"Strip."],[4108,4191,"I don't believe you."],[5288,5359,"Why did you try so hard"],[5359,5505,"to get into Calloway's class?"],[5672,5855,"I know I just started partying,"],[5855,6026,"but I came to college to learn."],[6097,6264,"And Professor Calloway's the best."],[6302,6431,"I would kill to get the last spot"],[6431,6539,"in her internship."],[6602,6690,"That's very"],[6760,6861,"admirable."],[7728,7811,"My turn."],[8033,8162,"You care about my brother"],[8162,8316,"more than you care about me."],[8495,8562,"Wrong."],[9905,9959,"Wait."]],"29":[[16,87,"Kaitlyn,"],[154,258,"I care about you"],[258,321,"differently."],[575,667,"You know the reason I"],[729,855,"basically lived at your house"],[855,1034,"when Ryan and I were in high school?"],[1330,1434,"My parents abused me."],[1672,1801,"Your family was the only reason,"],[1901,2022,"I ate dinner most nights."],[2189,2239,"And..."],[2427,2590,"they came to all my football games"],[2590,2665,"and cheered me on."],[2852,2973,"They helped me apply for law school."],[3086,3178,"I didn't know that,"],[3178,3228,"Cole."],[3336,3486,"I mean, you had every football team"],[3524,3641,"begging you to join and"],[3682,3795,"every law school in the country"],[3795,3920,"offering you a full ride."],[4045,4104,"I couldn't have done it"],[4104,4191,"without the Sinclairs."],[4346,4508,"So if I lose Ryan,"],[4558,4717,"I lose the only family I have."],[5105,5159,"Your turn."],[5609,5701,"You have feelings for me."]],"30":[[16,108,"You have feelings for me."],[1397,1601,"You finally got one right, Mr. Hart."],[1810,1956,"I have feelings for you."],[2231,2373,"Do you have feelings for me?"],[2673,2765,"I have"],[2823,2886,"very"],[2977,3090,"strong feelings for you."],[3224,3415,"So strong that it scares me."],[3645,3720,"I've never felt this way"],[3720,3816,"about a girl before."],[4024,4074,"My turn."],[4254,4383,"